  "Description": {
    "English": "A pack of luxury fireworks. These organic pyrotechnics rocket into the sky and explode in a splatter of slime, mucus, and wormlets. Ignite to create disgusting displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一捆奢华的烟花。这种有机火箭烟花可升入天空，引爆无数黏质、黏液和蠕虫，让血肉漫天飞溅。点燃就可以在天空中开启一场令人作呕的表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一整包豪華煙火。這種有機煙火能衝上天爆炸，造成整灘黏液、分泌物和蟲子飛濺。點燃即可在天空中製造令人作嘔的效果。<br><br>從<VAL_ON>建造選單<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>) 放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
